    <TextRegion id="r1" type="heading" custom="structure {type:heading;} label {Titel des Dokuments};">
      <Coords points="192,213 427,213 427,236 192,236" />
      <TextEquiv>
        <Unicode>THIS AGREEMENT
</Unicode>
      </TextEquiv>
    </TextRegion>
    <TextRegion id="r2" type="paragraph" custom="structure {type:paragraph;} label {Einleitungstext};">
      <Coords points="192,236 810,236 810,309 192,309" />
      <TextEquiv>
        <Unicode>is made this twelfth day of September, 1938 between Stefan Zweig of 49 Hallam
Street, London, W. 1., England, of the first part and Longmans, Green &amp; Co. Inc.,
of 114 Fifth Avenue, New York, N. Y. of the second part whereby it is mutually
agreed as follows:

1. The said Stefan Zweig agrees to furnish and deliver to the said Long-
mans, Green &amp; Co. Inc. not later than October 31, 1938 a treatise in the German</Unicode>
      </TextEquiv>
    </TextRegion>
    <TextRegion id="r3" type="list-label" custom="structure {type:list;} label {Vertragspunkt 1};">
      <Coords points="192,316 810,316 810,375 192,375" />
      <TextEquiv>
        <Unicode>language containing about six thousand words to be used as a preface in a work
which is to be published by the said Longmans, Green &amp; Co. Inc. entitled

THE LIVING THOUGHTS OF TOLSTOI
PRESENTED BY STEFAN ZWEIG

together with a condensation to run from thirty thousand (30,000) to thirty-</Unicode>
      </TextEquiv>
    </TextRegion>
    <TextRegion id="r4" type="heading" custom="structure {type:heading;} label {Buchtitel};">
      <Coords points="373,375 810,375 810,397 373,397" />
      <TextEquiv>
        <Unicode>five thousand (35,000) words, said condensation to be indicated in German
editions of Tolstoi's works, and a biography of Tolstoi of fifty to a hundred
words.</Unicode>
      </TextEquiv>
    </TextRegion>
    <TextRegion id="r5" type="paragraph" custom="structure {type:paragraph;} label {Fortsetzung Vertragspunkt 1};">
      <Coords points="192,397 810,397 810,442 192,442" />
      <TextEquiv>
        <Unicode>
2. The copyright in this treatise and condensation including all foreign
copyrights and all rights of translation and reproduction and all other rights
shall be the property of the said Longmans, Green &amp; Co. Inc. subject to the pay-
ment to the said Stefan Zweig of six hundred sixty-six dollars and sixty-seven</Unicode>
      </TextEquiv>
    </TextRegion>
    <TextRegion id="r6" type="list-label" custom="structure {type:list;} label {Vertragspunkt 2};">
      <Coords points="192,449 810,449 810,508 192,508" />
      <TextEquiv>
        <Unicode>cents ($666.67) to be paid on the acceptance of the manuscript by the said Long-
mans, Green &amp; Co. Inc.

3. The said Longmans, Green &amp; Co. Inc. shall be at liberty to deduct
from any payment, or payments, which may become due to the said Stefan Zweig
under this agreement any sum, or sums, which the said Longmans, Green &amp; Co. Inc.
shall be under statutory obligation to pay in respect of income tax.</Unicode>
      </TextEquiv>
    </TextRegion>
    <TextRegion id="r7" type="list-label" custom="structure {type:list;} label {Vertragspunkt 3};">
      <Coords points="192,515 810,515 810,559 192,559" />
      <TextEquiv>
        <Unicode>
4. The said Longmans, Green &amp; Co. Inc. will present to the said Stefan
Zweig upon publication, five (5) copies of the said work gratis.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF the parties hereto have hereunto subscribed their names</Unicode>
      </TextEquiv>
    </TextRegion>
    <TextRegion id="r8" type="list-label" custom="structure {type:list;} label {Vertragspunkt 4};">
      <Coords points="192,567 810,567 810,589 192,589" />
      <TextEquiv>
        <Unicode>and affixed their seals the day and year first above written.

In the presence of</Unicode>
      </TextEquiv>
    </TextRegion>
